# ASKN
# INSTALLED IN ARCHLINUX-INSTALLER
# yay -S  hyprland cpio meson cmake hyprland-qtutils xdg-desktop-portal-hyprland xdg-desktop-portal-gtk hyprlock hypridle hyprpicker

